{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Living there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Living there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was not the only thing because the flat was as well-- where we lived was in the-- pretty much in the center of Warsaw and in the kind of smart center of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a theater square where was the opera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a big theater really in the distance of one minute, and, and another square which is where-- which was a kind of a big, ceremonial square with palaces, and so only a distance of maybe two minutes.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was very exposed place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the result of that was, unfortunately, that we had-- that in this flat, we had quite a number of visits from the Germans already in this time in 1940.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would come, and they would look around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would requisition bits of furniture or bits of furniture or pictures or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they probably-- because we were-- and they knew that, that obviously, they had addresses of the Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, they came there a number of times and gave even my parents in the end, they took some furniture, and they took-- they requisitioned furniture.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They requisitioned pictures.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they gave my mother in the end a receipt saying that it all is going-- that she, she will get those things back at the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they gave a receipt, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh but there was nothing at the end of the war, obviously.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I, I don't think so, not-- because those people who came, they were probably-- well, I don't know who they were exactly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They probably were connected to the Gestapo or something like it or the military.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
